<item>
            <title>[SOLR-27] PATCH: Configurable language for SnowballPorterFilterFactory</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-27</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With this patch, the language used by SnowballPorterFilterFactory is configurable, for example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  &amp;lt;filter class=&quot;solr.SnowballPorterFilterFactory&quot; language=&quot;French&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Invalid languages will cause a ClassNotFoundException when the filter is created (so at search time possibly, not at initialization time).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12345976">SOLR-27</key>
            <summary>PATCH: Configurable language for SnowballPorterFilterFactory</summary>
